name: BETYdb
tagline: Web-interface to the Biofuel Ecophysiological Traits and Yields Database
body:
### BETYdb Development Website. 
BETYdb is a distributed system of databases used in agronomic and ecological research.
The primary portal is https://betydb.org. 
### Authors and Contributors 
* [BETYdb wiki](https://github.com/PecanProject/bety/wiki) for information on developing BETYdb.
* [Code of Conduct](https://pecanproject.github.io/bety/CODE_OF_CONDUCT) 
 * [Jobs](https://pecanproject.github.io/bety/jobs)
* [Open Issues](https://github.com/PecanProject/bety/issues)
